msgstr "Mesh 邻居节点"

msgid "Real-time batman-adv originator table. TQ: 255 = best. Refreshes every 5 seconds."
msgstr "实时 batman-adv 邻居表。TQ：255 为最佳。每 5 秒自动刷新。"

msgid "batman-adv originator table (batctl o). Neighbors appear when bat0 is running and at least one mesh backhaul link is active (wired LAN bridged, or 802.11s wireless mesh0). TQ 255=best link. Refreshes every 5s."
msgstr "batman-adv 邻居表（batctl o）。bat0 运行且至少有一条回程链路激活（有线 LAN 桥接或 802.11s 无线 mesh0）时才会出现邻居。TQ 255=最佳链路。每 5 秒刷新。"

msgid "EasyMesh daemon is not running. Enable EasyMesh and restart the service."
msgstr "EasyMesh 守护进程未运行，请在概览页面启用 EasyMesh 并重启服务。"

msgid "bat0 is not running. Try restarting the EasyMesh service."
msgstr "bat0 接口未启动，请尝试重启 EasyMesh 服务。"

msgid "No neighbors found. Verify all nodes share the same Mesh ID and password."
msgstr "未发现邻居节点。请确认所有节点已启用 EasyMesh 且 Mesh ID/密码完全一致。"

msgid "Link Quality (TQ)"
msgstr "链路质量（TQ）"

